baseName.value: Profiles for thermal break aluminium windows and doors: 3G NEO UP

generalComment.value:
The environmental performance associated with the product under investigation was assessed by considering primary data specific to the production process obtained through the dissemination of questionnaires to producers.


The results obtained are average consortium values, representative for the declared products and not for individual production units.


The criterion chosen for the initial inclusion of input and output elements is based on the definition of a 1% cut-off level, both in terms of mass and energy, per individual process.
